data.description: Welcome to your dream home, now with a new and improved price! This stunning Victorian-style gem offers the perfect blend of elegance and modern comfort. With 4 spacious bedrooms and 3.5 luxurious bathrooms, there's plenty of room for everyone to enjoy.    One of the standout features of this home is its recently replaced roof, ensuring worry-free living for years to come. Say goodbye to tedious yard work, as the HOA takes care of all the landscaping, allowing you to spend more time doing what you love.    Indulge in ultimate relaxation in the main floor primary suite, complete with a generously sized soaking tub, providing a serene escape from the outside world. The owner has spared no expense in updating this home, ensuring that it meets the highest standards of style and functionality.    This price improvement makes the home an even more attractive opportunity for discerning buyers looking for exceptional value. Don't miss out on the chance to make this exquisite Victorian-style residence your own. Schedule a viewing today and experience the charm and sophistication that awaits you! This home also qualifies for 100% financing!
